FastAPI + Supabase CRUD App with File Upload and Jinja2 Templates
This is a simple FastAPI CRUD application integrated with Supabase to store todo items. It supports:

âœ… Creating todos with title, description, and completed status

âœ… Uploading and streaming images/videos

âœ… Viewing todos on a Jinja2-powered HTML page

âœ… Serving static files like CSS

âœ… JSON API access for frontend/backend consumption

